---
import BaseLayout from '../layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title='Privacy Policy'>
  <section class='bg-white py-20 px-6 md:px-24'>
    <div class='max-w-5xl mx-auto'>
      <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-6 border-b pb-4'>Privacy Policy</h1>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to the Inuana Community Action Network (ICAN), a community
          organization based in Homa Bay Town, Homa Bay County, Kenya. We are
          committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency in how
          we handle your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how
          we collect, use, store, and protect your data when you visit our
          website or engage with our programs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>What Data We Collect</h2>
        <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1'>
          <li>
            <strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number,
            or address provided through membership forms, event registrations, or
            contact forms.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Website Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our
            website, such as IP addresses, browser type, and pages visited, collected
            via cookies or analytics tools like Google Analytics.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Voluntary Information:</strong> Feedback, survey responses, or
            messages you send us.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1'>
          <li>
            Manage memberships and send updates about ICAN’s programs and
            events.
          </li>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries or feedback.</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services through analytics.</li>
          <li>
            Comply with legal obligations under Kenya’s Data Protection Act,
            2019.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>Sharing Your Data</h2>
        <p class='mb-4'>
          We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties
          except:
        </p>
        <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1'>
          <li>
            <strong>Service Providers:</strong> Trusted third parties like email
            providers (e.g., Mailchimp) or analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics)
            that help us operate our website and programs. These providers are bound
            by contracts to protect your data.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect
            ICAN’s rights.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable measures to protect your data, including
          encryption, secure storage, and access controls. However, no online
          system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute
          security.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>Your Rights</h2>
        <p class='mb-4'>
          Under Kenya’s Data Protection Act, 2019, you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-1'>
          <li>Access your personal data we hold.</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data.</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict the processing of your data.</li>
          <li>Request data portability.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class='mb-10'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices
          or legal requirements. We will notify you of significant changes by
          posting the updated policy on our website with a new “Last updated”
          date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-2'>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your
          data, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <ul class='list-none mt-4 space-y-1'>
          <li><strong>Inuana Community Action Network (ICAN)</strong></li>
          <li>Homa Bay Town, Homa Bay County, Kenya</li>
          <li>
            Email: <a
              href='mailto:infolinkican@gmail.com'
              class='text-[#074351] hover:underline'>infolinkican@gmail.com</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>Phone: +254727455790, +254797451260</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
